<HEADLINE>
<P>
WOO WILL TEACH COURSE AT CALTECH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Former Los Angeles City Councilman Mike Woo will teach a class at Caltech this 
spring on politics. 
</P>
<P>
 Woo's class, "Asian Americans in Politics: From Private Identity to Public 
Responsibility," examines the motivations for political involvement, the 
obstacles that have prevented Asian Americans from being as successful in 
politics as they have in science and business, and the responsibility of 
professionals to become involved in their communities. 
</P>
