 Federated Allowed to Bid for Macy: Cyrus Vance, the court-appointed mediator 
for bankruptcy negotiations on R.H. Macy & Co., has given Federated Department 
Stores permission to propose a reorganization plan that calls for a merger of 
Federated and Macy. Vance said Federated can discuss its merger proposal with 
other Macy creditors and submit that reorganization plan to those creditors 
April 29. 
</P>
</TEXT>
