<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE TIMES TV INDEX: TV FACTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Nova science special "In Search of Human Origins" landed at the top of the 
list of PBS' 10 top-rated programs for March. The month's Top 10 PBS television 
