 Do It Big: Mandarin collars and delicate frog closures on white handkerchief 
linen are the signature details in the Krizia line. The Milan-based design 
house showed vests, jackets and long-sleeved, loose shirts over baggy 
drawstring pants. The shirt costs $465, the pants $380 at Neiman Marcus, 
Beverly Hills. The hat and sunglasses were made exclusively for the designer's 
fashion show. 
</P>
