</P>
<P>
 9 a.m. to 4 p.m., United Way, 6851 Lennox Ave., Van Nuys. Call (818) 
908-5107.. 
</P>
<P>
 7 a.m. to 12:30 p.m., Westlake Medical Center, 4415 S. Lakeview Canyon Road. 
Call (818) 706-6163. 
</P>
