<TEXT>
<P>
 A domestic dispute between an estranged couple in the 800 block of South 
Cypress Avenue left both parties hospitalized with serious injuries Thursday, 
police said. 
</P>
<P>
 The fight began when Vertaldo Victerio Cestelan, 48, arrived at the home of 
Josefina Lucero Madin, said Sgt. Dick Faust. In the ensuing melee, Cestelan and 
Lucero attacked each other with knives and two bedposts, Faust said. 
</P>
