 Bell-Jeff 15, St. Genevieve 0 -- Carrie Breedlove pitched a one-hitter, 
striking out 15 in a Camino Real League game shortened to five innings because 
of the 10-run rule. 
</P>
<P>
 Montclair Prep 5, Alverno 3 -- Tami Freedman doubled and hit a two-run home 
run, her sixth, to highlight a come-from-behind victory. Jodi Gelfand also had 
two hits and two RBIs. BOYS' TRACK 
</P>
